Package com.zoubworld.java.utils.compress.file

Interface IBinaryReader

All Known Implementing Classes:
BinaryFinFout, BinaryPipeAlgo, BinaryStdIn
public interface IBinaryReader
Author:
Pierre Valleau This interface is used to support read of any basic type of data on a storage object/file. byte, char,short,int, long string, float,double,Icode,Isymbol,n bits.

      char readChar()
      Reads the next 8 bits from standard input and return as an 8-bit char. Note that char is a 16-bit type; to read the next 16 bits as a char, use readChar(16).
      Returns:
      the next 8 bits of data from standard input as a char
